sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Candidato (bluee.localhost)
  participant FE as Front Jobs
  participant BFF as back-bluee
  participant ORG as organizations (RMQ)
  participant USR as users/auth (RMQ)
  participant DB as MongoDB

  C->>FE: POST /jobs/signup (email, name, password)
  FE->>BFF: GET /organizations/public/by-slug/:slug
  BFF->>ORG: RMQ organizations.get-by-slug
  ORG->>DB: findOne identity.slug
  ORG-->>BFF: organization (_id tenantId)
  FE->>BFF: POST /auth/jobs/signup (tenantId + credenciales)
  BFF->>USR: RMQ auth.signup-candidate
  USR->>DB: create user role=candidate, tenantId
  USR-->>BFF: user creado
  BFF-->>FE: ok

  C->>FE: POST /jobs/login
  FE->>BFF: POST /auth/jobs/login
  BFF->>USR: RMQ auth.login
  USR->>DB: validate credenciales + emitir tokens
  USR-->>BFF: access/refresh + roles
  BFF->>BFF: valida role=candidate
  BFF-->>FE: set cookies httpOnly + sesión jobs

